    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(239, 61, 37);">EI</span></p>
    <p is="qowt-word-para" style="display: block; list-style-type: none; padding: 0px 0px 0pt; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, Carlito, sans-serif;"><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Sous cette forme juridique, l&rsquo;entreprise et l&rsquo;entrepreneur ne forment qu&rsquo;une seule et m&ecirc;me personne ; le patrimoine professionnel et personnel&nbsp;</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">sont</span><span is="qowt-word-run" style="display: inline; white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;juridiquement confondus et l&rsquo;entrepreneur se trouve personnellement responsable des dettes de l&rsquo;entreprise.&nbsp;</span></p>
